revision.text: '''Pinkan''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in the [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding a empty plot with one of all pink color berries found before it in berridex ([[Pecha]], [[Persim]], [[Nanab]], [[Mago]], [[Qualot]], [[Magost]] and [[Watmel]]) .
revision.comment: Importing a new version from external source
